{"tid":781244,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大家對fresh grad要求係點","createTime":"2018-08-15T17:50:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-15T18:39:15.000Z","uid":125275,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"82120a3708fd1bb42416aad1cd678a31a456f66e","tid":781244,"uid":125275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T17:50:09.000Z","msg":"話說我做野都幾年<br />\n今年黎左個fresh grad <br />\n其實佢人幾好 都好相處 <br />\n做野都快都爽手 但係有時會錯d minor野<br />\n例如打錯標點呀之類<br />\n今日見佢打錯左個標點比阿頭毒鬧 都鬧得好甘 又粗口又剩咁 <br />\n但我地平時錯 就不嬲無事嘅<br />\n其實對fresh grad係咪真係要咁嚴呢<br />\n我當年啱啱畢業果間嘅阿頭都對我都好體諒<br />\n始終第一年出黎做野邊有可能識曬<br />\n巴打們點睇 <br />\n其實阿頭咁對個fg係咪純想發洩<br />\n定係想教識佢？"},{"pid":"0201cdaba7cead6706bd8c9649ff9f262874f042","tid":781244,"uid":69083,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T18:13:24.000Z","msg":"咩野工打錯標點要毒閙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c2b857cfc9ffc1e89c8ded30bdf6142fd7dbc1b","tid":781244,"uid":125275,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"0201cdaba7cead6706bd8c9649ff9f262874f042","tid":781244,"uid":69083,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T18:13:24.000Z","msg":"咩野工打錯標點要毒閙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T18:36:22.000Z","msg":"做d page <br />\n個page接觸嘅人都多 <br />\n唔講太details haha"},{"pid":"c89edb145e5f1493b31091eb9a73d55500ac32af","tid":781244,"uid":98223,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T18:39:15.000Z","msg":"要乜撚都識 好似做左好耐野咁 然後任勞任怨 死貓孭哂就梗架啦"}]}